Author: gimmethatdamnavocado
Text: I deleted it multiple times but it doesn’t help because my brain is so good at keeping track I don’t even need the app. So I downloaded it again...

Author: DavidFrumTheBlock
Text: This is me.    I redownloaded the app because counting calories obsessively and doing math problems mentally based on my intake, TDEE and activity all fucking day long really fills my days up.
